1934;;The Most Precious Thing in Life;;American;;Lambert Hillyer;;Richard Cromwell, Jean Arthur;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Most_Precious_Thing_in_Life;;Ellen Holmes, a girl from an ordinary family, marries a rich, yet spoiled, boy from a snobbish family. The pair has a son, but soon Ellen finds herself ousted from the life of her husband. However, she rediscovers her son years later.[5]